# Screenshots Directory

Store test screenshots here organized by date:

```
screenshots/
├── 2024-11-17/
│   ├── kish-grid-1.1-single-member-pass.png
│   ├── gps-3.6-within-threshold-pass.png
│   └── ...
├── 2024-11-18/
│   └── ...
```

## Naming Convention

`[section]-[test-number]-[description]-[status].png`

Examples:
- `kish-grid-1.1-single-member-pass.png`
- `gps-3.6-within-threshold-fail.png`
- `offline-5.3-sync-error.png`
